mtu. Ruby on Rails, or Rails, is 
server-side web application 
framework written in Ruby under the
MIT License. Rails is a model–
view–controller (MVC) framework,
providingproviding default structures for a database, a web service, and web pages. It encourages and facilitates the use of web standards such as JSON or XML for data transfer, HTML, CSS and JavaScript for user interfacing. In addition to MVC, Rails emphasizes the use of other well-known software engineering patterns and paradigms,
including convention 
